'''抗蛇毒血清'''是一种治疗因咬伤和蜇伤（例如被蜘蛛咬伤、被蛇咬伤、被鱼蜇伤和被蝎子蜇伤<ref name=BNF69>{{cite book|title=British national formulary : BNF 69|url=https://archive.org/details/bnf69britishnati0000unse|date=2015|publisher=British Medical Association|isbn=9780857111562|page=[https://archive.org/details/bnf69britishnati0000unse/page/43 43]|edition=69}}</ref> ）而感染[[毒液|毒液]]的特异性药物，內有[[抗體|抗體]]，且抗蛇毒血清有嚴重副作用，例如[[血清病|血清病]]、[[呼吸困难|呼吸困难]]和[[過敏性休克|過敏性休克]]，因此除非毒液毒性很高，一般情況下不推薦使用。<ref name=WHO2008>{{cite book | title = WHO Model Formulary 2008 | year = 2009 | isbn = 9789241547659 | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | veditors = Stuart MC, Kouimtzi M, Hill SR | hdl = 10665/44053 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization |pages=396–397}}</ref>

抗蛇毒血清傳統製作過程是先通过收集相关动物的毒液<ref name=Dar2004/>，然後将少量的毒液注射到家畜身上，使得家畜產生抗體，然后从家畜的血液中收集抗体并进行纯化。<ref name=Dar2004>{{cite book|last1=Dart|first1=Richard C.|title=Medical Toxicology|date=2004|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=9780781728454|pages=250–251|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BfdighlyGiwC&pg=PA250|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109184820/https://books.google.ca/books?id=BfdighlyGiwC&pg=PA250|archive-date=2017-01-09}}</ref>由于生产抗蛇毒血清的成本较高，且在不冷藏的情况下保质期较短，目前研究人員正在积极探索更好的生产抗蛇毒血清的方法。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6073149/ |title=Recent Advances in Next Generation Snakebite Antivenoms |access-date=2021-01-13 |archive-date=2022-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220331060624/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6073149/ }}</ref> 

人類從19世纪末開始研制抗蛇毒血清，最早由法国细菌学家[[阿尔贝·卡尔梅特|阿尔贝·卡尔梅特]]研发<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Doctor Albert Calmette 1863-1933: founder of antivenomous serotherapy and of antituberculous BCG vaccination|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10400286/|last=Hawgood|first=B. J.|date=1999-09|journal=Toxicon: Official Journal of the International Society on Toxinology|issue=9|doi=10.1016/s0041-0101(99)00086-0|volume=37|pages=1241–1258|issn=0041-0101|pmid=10400286|access-date=2021-02-10|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116211843/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10400286/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Antivenom|url=https://www.si.edu/spotlight/antibody-initiative/antivenom|accessdate=2021-02-10|work=Smithsonian Institution|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212234930/https://www.si.edu/spotlight/antibody-initiative/antivenom|dead-url=no}}</ref>，20世纪50年代抗蛇毒血清开始普及。<ref name=Dar2004/><ref>{{cite book|last1=Gad|first1=Shayne Cox|title=Handbook of Pharmaceutical Biotechnology|date=2007|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9780470117101|page=692|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZhlApPkxpuAC&pg=PA692|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109185439/https://books.google.ca/books?id=ZhlApPkxpuAC&pg=PA692|archive-date=2017-01-09}}</ref>目前抗蛇毒血清被列入[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]。<ref name="WHO21st">{{cite book | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | title = World Health Organization model list of essential medicines: 21st list 2019 | year = 2019 | hdl = 10665/325771 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | location = Geneva | id = WHO/MVP/EMP/IAU/2019.06. License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 IGO | hdl-access=free }}</ref>

